The targets of natural isotopic composition used in the
present experiments were self-supporting metallic films
of 1-10 mg/cm2 thickness, prepared by mechanical
rolling.  The layer thicknesses have been determined by
weighing and by energy-loss measurements with alpha
particles.  The non-uniformity has been investigated by
energy-loss measurements afar from the target centre.
